ublican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|1978\u20131979\n|[[Julian Carroll]]\n|[[Kentucky]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|1979\u20131980\n|[[Otis R. Bowen|Otis Bowen]]\n|[[Indiana]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|1980\u20131981\n|[[George Busbee]]\n|[[Georgia (U.S. state)|Georgia]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|1981\u20131982\n|[[Richard A. Snelling|Richard Snelling]]\n|[[Vermont]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|1982\u20131983\n|[[Scott M. Matheson|Scott Matheson]]\n|[[Utah]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|1983\u20131984\n|[[James R. Thompson|Jim Thompson]]\n|[[Illinois]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|1984\u20131985\n|[[John W. Carlin|John Carlin]]\n|[[Kansas]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|1985\u20131986\n|[[Lamar Alexander]]\n|[[Tennessee]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|1986\u20131987\n|[[Bill Clinton]]\n|[[Arkansas]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|1987\u20131988\n|[[John H. Sununu|John Sununu]]\n|[[New Hampshire]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|1988\u20131989\n|[[Gerald L. Baliles|Gerald Baliles]]\n|[[Virginia]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|1989\u20131990\n|[[Terry Branstad]]\n|[[Iowa]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|1990\u20131991\n|[[Booth Gardner]]\n|[[Washington (state)|Washington]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|1991\u20131992\n|[[John Ashcroft]]\n|[[Missouri]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|1992\u20131993\n|[[Roy Romer]]\n|[[Colorado]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United