 Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|2009\u20132010\n|[[Jim Douglas]]\n|[[Vermont]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|2010\n|[[Joe Manchin]]\n|[[West Virginia]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|2010\u20132011\n|[[Christine Gregoire]]\n|[[Washington (state)|Washington]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|2011\u20132012\n|[[Dave Heineman]]\n|[[Nebraska]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|2012\u20132013\n|[[Jack Markell]]\n|[[Delaware]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|2013\u20132014\n|[[Mary Fallin]]\n|[[Oklahoma]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|2014\u20132015\n|[[John Hickenlooper]]\n|[[Colorado]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|2015\u20132016\n|[[Gary Herbert]]\n|[[Utah]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|2016\u20132017\n|[[Terry McAuliffe]]\n|[[Virginia]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|2017\u20132018\n|[[Brian Sandoval]]\n|[[Nevada]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|2018\u20132019\n|[[Steve Bullock (American politician)|Steve Bullock]]\n|[[Montana]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|2019\u2013present\n|[[Larry Hogan]]\n|[[Maryland]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|}\n\n==See also==\n*[[Council of Australian Governments]], similar body in [[Australia]]\n*[[Joint Ministerial Committee (UK)]], similar body in the [[United Kingdom]]\n*[[First Ministers' conference]], similar body in [[Canada]]\n*[[National Governors Conference (Mexico)]], similar organization in Mexico\n*[[United States Conference of Mayors]]\n*[[Republican Governors Association]]\n*[[Democratic Governors Association]]\n*[[Governors Highway S